  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/09f2b0db4e6ff7344596c6a446616202.poster.avif?t=1631157474\" width=562 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/09f2b0db4e6ff7344596c6a446616202.webm?t=1631157474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/09f2b0db4e6ff7344596c6a446616202.mp4?t=1631157474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>30 cute and unique bosses are waiting for you in a colorful world of pixel art.<br>But don't let your guard down just because they're cute! These bosses shoot lots of bullets!<br><br>The hail of bullets might look hard.<br>But don't worry.<br>With special bullets that catch your opponent's bullets, you can shoot them all back!<br>The more you catch, the stronger you get!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/822329cd162165252b9f933fd1efd05e.poster.avif?t=1631157474\" width=562 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/822329cd162165252b9f933fd1efd05e.webm?t=1631157474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/822329cd162165252b9f933fd1efd05e.mp4?t=1631157474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Perfect for people who like cute things and want a game they can start enjoying right away.<br></li><li>30 unique bosses!<br></li><li>8 playable characters with different abilities!<br></li><li>Supercute chiptune soundtrack!</li></ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/c9d1468262aacc4e09d38a08800edcc9.poster.avif?t=1631157474\" width=562 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/c9d1468262aacc4e09d38a08800edcc9.webm?t=1631157474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338020/extras/c9d1468262aacc4e09d38a08800edcc9.mp4?t=1631157474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
